<html>
<head>
<title>Event Table</title>
<style>
table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; }
th, td { border: 1px solid black; padding: 8px; text-align: left; }
th { background-color: #f2f2f2; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>2.2 Event Table</h1>
<table>
<tr>
<th>Event ID</th>
<th>Event Name</th>
<th>Trigger</th>
<th>Source</th>
<th>Activity</th>
<th>Response</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-001</td>
<td>User Joins Room</td>
<td>User selects/enters room</td>
<td>Client App</td>
<td>Join Socket Room</td>
<td>Broadcast join confirmation</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-002</td>
<td>Message Sent</td>
<td>User clicks send button</td>
<td>Client App</td>
<td>Encrypt & Encode Message</td>
<td>Send to server, save locally</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-003</td>
<td>Message Received</td>
<td>Socket message event</td>
<td>Server</td>
<td>Decode & Decrypt Message</td>
<td>Display in chat, play sound</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-004</td>
<td>Typing Started</td>
<td>User types in input</td>
<td>Client App</td>
<td>Emit typing start</td>
<td>Show typing indicator to others</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-005</td>
<td>Typing Stopped</td>
<td>User stops typing (timeout)</td>
<td>Client App</td>
<td>Emit typing stop</td>
<td>Hide typing indicator</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-006</td>
<td>Settings Changed</td>
<td>User updates username/key/room</td>
<td>Client App</td>
<td>Save to LocalStorage</td>
<td>Update UI and reconnect if needed</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-007</td>
<td>Image Selected</td>
<td>User selects image file</td>
<td>Client App</td>
<td>Validate file size</td>
<td>Enable send button</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-008</td>
<td>Secret Mode Toggle</td>
<td>User triple-clicks header</td>
<td>Client App</td>
<td>Switch between cover/chat mode</td>
<td>Change UI view</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-009</td>
<td>Message History Loaded</td>
<td>Room changes</td>
<td>Client App</td>
<td>Query IndexedDB</td>
<td>Display saved messages</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>EVT-010</td>
<td>Connection Lost</td>
<td>Network disconnect</td>
<td>Browser</td>
<td>Attempt reconnection</td>
<td>Show offline status</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p><strong>Notes:</strong> All events are handled asynchronously where appropriate. Local storage events are synchronous. Socket events are real-time and bidirectional.</p>
</body>
</html>
